Contents

| File                     | Description |
|--------------------------|-------------|
| `Algorithms.java`        | Implements core algorithms: Bubble Sort, Insertion Sort, and Linear Search. |
| `Main.java`              | Entry point of the application. Accepts user input, runs selected algorithms, and records execution time. |


Algorithms Implemented

1. Bubble Sort
- Best Case: O(n) – Already sorted
- Worst Case: O(n²) – Reverse sorted
- Average Case: O(n²)

2. Insertion Sort
- Best Case: O(n) – Already sorted
- Worst Case: O(n²) – Reverse sorted
- Average Case: O(n²)

3. Linear Search
- Best Case: O(1) – First element
- Worst Case: O(n) – Last element or not found
- Average Case: O(n/2)



How to Run

Compile
```bash
javac KimathiSedegah_22237205/*.java
